 style=\"color: #000000;\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp;Event organization (mainly, getting queries for conferences);</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp;Arrangement of team-building activities for MICE groups</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp;Arrangement of meals, Gala Programs in different authentic environments</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp;Incentive, special interest groups, destination weddings</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp;Tours to all touristic sites in selected destinations</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp;Largest variability of entertainment options in all destinations</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp;Camping services</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp;Visa support</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'SERVICES', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '156-2', '', '', '2019-06-24 06:49:09', '2019-06-24 06:49:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/toursntravel/?page_id=156', 0, 'page', '', 0),
